parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission shifting issues can cause the vehicle to jerk or hesitate, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission shifts extremely hard in and out of gear
the vehicle has trouble slowing down
the vehicle has difficulty shifting up or down in gears
the vehicle won't go into gear
the transmission bucks and surges at low speeds.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear differential can cause the vehicle to hesitate or lose power, making it difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates on the highway
the vehicle loses speed
the vehicle makes a whining or grinding noise.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch hydraulic system can cause the clutch pedal to stick to the floor, making it difficult or impossible to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the adaptive cruise control system can cause the vehicle to fail to slow down or stop, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: The dash shows a car in the path
but there is a 2-3 second delay before the car starts to slow down
the brakes do not engage
the alarms go off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Various issues with the vehicle's systems can cause unexpected noises, vibrations, or malfunctions, which can be distracting and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle makes a clanking sound
the vehicle jerks with a loud noise
the instrument panel lights fade in and out
the outside temperature display is incorrect
a tapping noise can be heard coming from the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The constant illumination of the side detection lights in the side mirrors can cause distractions while driving, potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: The side detection lights in the side mirrors remain on even when the vehicle is turned off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The cracked CUE display screen can obstruct the driver's view, causing a safety hazard while driving, especially when using the backup camera.
symptoms: The CUE display screen has cracks or "spiderweb" cracks
making the touch screen unusable
and causing the display to frequently blink and emit random audio tones.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A vehicle fire can cause serious injuries or fatalities, as well as damage to property.
symptoms: The vehicle catches on fire while driving
with smoke and flames emanating from the front hood.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: A dead battery can leave the driver stranded, and repeated failures can cause inconvenience and safety concerns.
symptoms: The vehicle won't start
and the battery is completely drained
with no cells and unable to be charged.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear differential can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, and may render the vehicle unsafe to drive.
symptoms: Abnormal roaring or howling noise from the wheels
rear end of the vehicle lowering
difficulty driving
warning lights may not be illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to lose power, shut down, and experience various malfunctions, which can lead to accidents, injuries, or strand the driver.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
the steering wheel becomes inoperable
the accelerator sticks
the fuel shuts off
the vehicle shuts down multiple times while driving
the CUE screen malfunctions
the air conditioning switches to heat
the windows roll down randomly
the speedometer goes off and then comes back on
and other electrical issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to lose power steering, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The power steering message is displayed
the power steering fails to engage
the vehicle is difficult to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the battery can cause the vehicle to fail to start, which can leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The battery becomes inoperable
the vehicle fails to start.
